<lb ed="I" n="0031a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>嵩顯寺碑</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0031a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0031a0101">敕賜
<lb ed="I" n="0031a02" type="honorific"/>嵩顯
<lb ed="I" n="0031a03" type="honorific"/>禪寺
<lb ed="I" n="0031a04" type="honorific"/>碑記</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0031b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0031b0101">□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b02" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">神</unclear>□□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">不</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">夜</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">者</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">也</unclear>□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">垂</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">慈</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">暉</unclear>□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">上</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">久</unclear>□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b03" type="honorific"/>化於億載□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">下</unclear>。大千燭<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">茲</unclear>昏□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">且</unclear>隱顯弗恒契乎。□□□□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b04" type="honorific"/>非運資廣因。樹應曩世。豈能開扇道風。施沾法雨者哉。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">仰</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">惟</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0031b05" type="honorific"/>皇帝陛下。纂統重光。紹隆累聖。德洽三才。道均五緯。政極<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">辰</unclear>□。□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">乃</unclear>□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b06" type="honorific"/>源。遊神法菀。慧鼓既振。普天聞般若之音。頹綱更開。率土悟火宅<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b07" type="honorific"/>場斯趣矣。自惟<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0031001" n="0031001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0031001" n="0031001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0031001" n="0031001"/>啓<anchor xml:id="end0031001"/>蹤。冀方樹基。勃海并世。□宛著姓。神州靈降。盛□□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b08" type="honorific"/>淂戚聯。朝旭昵親<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">夕</unclear><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0031002" n="0031002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0031002" n="0031002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0031002" n="0031002"/>容<anchor xml:id="end0031002"/>。內秉望舒之讚。外憖阿衡之翼。入<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">總</unclear>謀<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">議</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">出</unclear>□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b09" type="honorific"/>沖波坤津潛液寒。族貫春日之榮幽。附沾夏辰之蔚輝。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">顯</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">哉</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">而</unclear>□□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b10" type="honorific"/>渥而溳心罔謝。遂仰慕皇緯報施之功。亦尋聖經緣果之旨。□詳<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">群</unclear>□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b11" type="honorific"/>蘭厥靈岑。擇茲飃嶺。上涌沖天之峰。下帶□岫之險。重<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">基</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">雲</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">構</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">飛</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">級</unclear>□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b12" type="honorific"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0031003" n="0031003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0031003" n="0031003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0031003" n="0031003"/>槃<anchor xml:id="end0031003"/>屈虯電暐豔琨成。瑍若資神。乃□□質沉。堅翠□外。□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">麗</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">炎</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">新</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">至</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">在</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0031b13" type="honorific"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0031004" n="0031004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0031004" n="0031004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0031004" n="0031004"/>希<anchor xml:id="end0031004"/>世之相。千像吐琦。万形挺妙。苕苕焉。暉赫萃乎<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">兆</unclear>日。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">修</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">修</unclear>焉。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">感</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">發</unclear>□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b14" type="honorific"/>斯誠。冀微功鍾於至德。顯福應於道祚。述遵休風。遂興<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">頌</unclear>曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0031b15" type="honorific"/>修哉渾源。冥化琨成。道氣既開。□像垂形。紛華競耀。至猷<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">淹</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">經</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">聖</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">覺</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">匪</unclear>□。□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b16" type="honorific"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0031005" n="0031005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0031005" n="0031005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0031005" n="0031005"/>恢<anchor xml:id="end0031005"/><anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>恢<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>至謨。苕苕遐宣。道流三界。化溢大千。幽衢<anchor xml:id="beg_2" type="star"/>啓<anchor xml:id="end_2"/>轍。靜<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">境</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">亟</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">埏</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">隱</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">顯</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">弗</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">恒</unclear>□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b17" type="honorific"/>聖皇沖感。靈液遐融。潤均法海。扇協道風。悟因訓<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">萃</unclear>。果隨<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">業</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">崇</unclear>。□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">區</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">萇</unclear>□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b18" type="honorific"/>靈降盛德。二后經綸。內光椒掖。外允九臣。齊思渭陽。嘉爵交<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">臻</unclear>。誓被□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b19" type="honorific"/>沉<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0031006" n="0031006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0031006" n="0031006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0031006" n="0031006"/>谿<anchor xml:id="end0031006"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">賁</unclear>壑。峰山霄星。風雲交液。吐化蚕類。玄堂暐豔。聖容<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">啟</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">靈</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">樹</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">銘</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">興</unclear>□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0031b20" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">大</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">魏</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">永</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">平</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">二</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">年</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">歲</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">在</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">己</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">丑</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">四</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">月</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">戊</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">申</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">朔</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">八</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">日</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">乙</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">卯</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">使</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">持</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">節</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">都</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">督</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">涇</unclear>□□□□□</p>
</cb:div>
